    "description": "《Worldless》的背景设定在一个新生宇宙，其中实体受互相吸引的极性所限，陷入了永恒的冲突中。这些相互作用会导致极性交换，但这个过程非常不稳定，谁知道会产生什么新的结果……<br><br>在这款2D动态时间回合制平台游戏中，玩家将探索错综复杂、充满秘密和奥秘的互联区域，还可以使用冲刺和墙跳等多种技能。<br><br>在探索过程中，你会遭遇不同的生命体，它们意图阻止你在这个宇宙中寻找自己的位置。在回合制规则下，对抗将传统战斗与动态时间动作相结合，带来了惊心动魄的战略性战斗，你对游戏机制和技能的了解将面临考验。<br><br><strong>确立自我</strong> <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 揭示无法想象的可能性：在抽象的区域中跳跃和冲刺，追求超越。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898500/extras/218494041517f7e3dbe29ec10a3411d4.poster.avif?t=1758539643\" width=780 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898500/extras/218494041517f7e3dbe29ec10a3411d4.webm?t=1758539643\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898500/extras/218494041517f7e3dbe29ec10a3411d4.mp4?t=1758539643\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br> <br><strong> 为生存而成长</strong> <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>通过错综复杂、有回报的天赋树升级你的技能<br></li><li>有备无患：参与动态时间回合制战斗，完美拿捏攻击和防御时机来粉碎敌人。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898500/extras/e0c565923764287e00a76ba33371408e.poster.avif?t=1758539643\" width=780 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898500/extras/e0c565923764287e00a76ba33371408e.webm?t=1758539643\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898500/extras/e0c565923764287e00a76ba33371408e.mp4?t=1758539643\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br> <br><strong> 沉浸其中</strong> <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>迷人旋律：通过令人难忘的优美配乐，在更深的层次中融入《Worldless》的各个区域。<br></li><li>珍惜当下：在神秘而迷人的叙事中定义这个世界，并挑战其秘密。。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898500/extras/d4e7237520c9b58fdd21b8a56b435ee8.poster.avif?t=1758539643\" width=780 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898500/extras/d4e7237520c9b58fdd21b8a56b435ee8.webm?t=1758539643\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898500/extras/d4e7237520c9b58fdd21b8a56b435ee8.mp4?t=1758539643\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
